<li class="toclevel-1 tocsection-3"><a href="#Часть_3"><span class="tocnumber">3</span> <span class="toctext">Часть 3</span></a></li>
<li class="toclevel-1 tocsection-4"><a href="#Часть_4"><span class="tocnumber">4</span> <span class="toctext">Часть 4</span></a></li>
